    " On some systems SmartHome doesn't work without it.
    " Below is similar (but not exactly the same!) solution as https://vi.stackexchange.com/questions/12325/why-cant-i-set-home-or-t-kh-in-my-vimrc-file
    set <xHome>=[1~
    set <kHome>=[1~
    set <xEnd>=[4~
    set <kEnd>=[4~
